org.rsna.ctp.pipeline

Class AbstractPipelineStage

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.rsna.ctp.pipeline.AbstractPipelineStage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PipelineStage
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractImportService, AbstractQueuedExportService, ArchiveImportService, BasicFileStorageService, DatabaseVerifier, DicomAnonymizer, DicomAuditLogger, DicomCorrector, DicomDecompressor, DicomDifferenceLogger, DicomFilter, DicomMammoPixelAnonymizer, DicomPaletteImageConverter, DicomPixelAnonymizer, DicomPlanarConfigurationConverter, DicomTranscoder, DirectoryStorageService, EmailService, FileStorageService, IDMap, LookupTableChecker, MemoryMonitor, ObjectCache, ObjectLogger, ObjectTracker, PerformanceLogger, XmlAnonymizer, XmlFilter, ZipAnonymizer, ZipFilter

    public abstract class AbstractPipelineStage
extends java.lang.Object
implements PipelineStage
    An abstract class implementing the PipelineStage interface. This class instantiates the Quarantine if one is specified. It also captures the root attribute and makes the directory if necessary. It also supplies an implementation of the getName and getConfigHTML methods. Subclasses can depend on those methods but must override the getStatusHTML method to provide status relevant to the PipelineStage being implemented.
